welcome_message_title: Welcome to La Victoria de Acentejo
welcome_message_body: "Welcome to La Victoria de Acentejo, Spain! Get ready to experience the charming atmosphere of this beautiful city, known for its stunning scenery and delicious local cuisine. We invite you to explore and immerse yourself in all that La Victoria has to offer. Enjoy your stay!"
